---json
{
    "layout": "base.njk",
    "type": "website",
    "title": "Climate Research Notes",
    "addTitleSuffix": true
}
---

<main id="climate">

    <h1>Climate research notes</h1>

    <aside id="research-note-preface">
        These are personal research notes on the drivers, impacts of, and potential solutions to climate change. In 2019, I decided to shift from virtual and augmented reality to climate change, hoping to find a place where I could make a positive contribution. These notes are written primarily for myself, so many will be brief, incomplete, etc. But hopefully they (and/or the references) are useful.
    </aside>

    <section id="highlights">
        <h2>Highlights</h2>
        <ul class="highlights">
            {%- for post in collections.climate -%}
                {% if post.data.highlight %}
                    <li>
                        <a href="{{ post.url }}">
                            {% if post.data.image %}
                                <img src="/img/{{ post.data.image }}">
                            {% endif %}
                        </a>

                        <h4>
                            <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
                        </h4>

                        {% if post.data.summary %}
                            <p>{{ post.data.summary }}</p>
                        {% endif %}

                        <time datetime="{{ post.modified }}">Last updated {{ post.modified | date("D MMM YYYY") }}</time>
                    </li>
                {% endif %}
            {%- endfor -%}
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="all">
        <h2>All notes</h2>
        <h3 id="impacts">Impacts</h3>
        <ul>
            {%- for post in collections.climateImpacts -%}
                <li>
                    <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
                </li>
            {%- endfor -%}
        </ul>
        <h3 id="canada">Canada</h3>
        <ul>
            {%- for post in collections.climateImpactsCanada -%}
                <li>
                    <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
                </li>
            {%- endfor -%}
        </ul>
        <h3 id="solutions">Solutions</h3>
        <ul>
            {%- for post in collections.climateSolutions -%}
                <li>
                    <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
                </li>
            {%- endfor -%}
        </ul>
        <h3 id="resiliency">Resiliency</h3>
        <ul>
            {%- for post in collections.climateResiliency -%}
                <li>
                    <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
                </li>
            {%- endfor -%}
        </ul>
    </section>

</main>

